Package: llamacppR
Type: Package
Title: Minimal R bindings for llama.cpp (CPU)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Justin", family = "Savoie", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "justin@example.com"))
Description: Lightweight R wrapper for llama.cpp's simple example using only CPU.
    Vendors the llama.cpp source and builds a static library via CMake during
    package compilation. Provides a single function to generate text from a prompt.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
SystemRequirements: CMake (>= 3.20), C++17 toolchain
NeedsCompilation: yes
Depends: R (>= 3.6)
Suggests: 
URL: https://github.com/justinsavoie/llamacppR
BugReports: https://github.com/justinsavoie/llamacppR/issues
